      <title>超级丰收带来的提振效应减弱，巴西经济陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/brazil-s-economy-stalls-at-end-of-2023-in-worrying-sign-for-lula</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西经济连续第二个季度陷入停滞，原因是消费者控制支出以及强劲作物产量的提振作用消退，这可能预示着总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦未来的日子会更加艰难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/brazil-s-economy-stalls-at-end-of-2023-in-worrying-sign-for-lula</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 12:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
